                <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 12px;">Required once per project to enable the Database Extensions.</p>
                <button class="btn-outline" style="border-color: var(--ai-accent); color: var(--ai-accent); font-size: 11px;" onclick="enableCronExtensions()">Enable pg_cron & pg_net</button>
